    • 构造器详细资料

      • SftpPool

        public SftpPool(SftpFactory factory,
                SftpPoolConfig config,
                SftpAbandonedConfig abandonedConfig)
        Creates a new GenericObjectPool that tracks and destroys objects that are checked out, but never returned to the pool. 创建一个GenericObjectPool对象池，跟踪使用后未返回给对象池的对象，防止对象泄漏。
        参数:
        factory - The object factory to be used to create object instances used by this pool 对象工厂
        config - The base pool configuration to use for this pool instance. The configuration is used by value. Subsequent changes to the configuration object will not be reflected in the pool. 对象池配置
        abandonedConfig - Configuration for abandoned object identification 废弃对象跟踪配置
